data.description: NEWLY REMOLDED * BIG LOT ONE ACRE* HUGE TWO STORY GARAGE * Explore your options! Freedom Awaits!! NO HOA This home is a MUST SEE, completely renovated home peacefully residing in Loris with ample privacy and space on almost an acre has plenty of parking for your camper or boat. The home has covered porch, attached 1 car garage, a first floor master suite, and has been equipped with a new roof, new luxury vinyl plank floors, granite countertops, all new tiled walk in showers, vaulted ceilings, new recessed can lights and light fixtures, brand new white shaker cabinets with soft close drawers, as well as new stainless steel appliances. Come on home and start making memories with your loved ones. The oversized 1450 sqft. detached 2 car garage has been equipped with a new electrical panel and lighting, there is also a possible living space upstairs, for an in-law-suite rent it out to offset costs, or make it the site of your home business. The possibilities are endless when you have the space readily available  under 2 miles to Hwy 9 and the Tractor Supply, 3 miles to Food Lion, CVS pharm. and 25 miles to Cherry Grove Beach Atlantic Ocean. This home has the best of both worlds close to the all the beach amenities, water sports, fishing, boating, sunbathing on the sand, world class golf courses, Outlet shopping, live entertainment, many restaurants for any budget and when you have had your feel of the beach life drive 20-25 min home to your peaceful country homestead and relax until the  notion strikes you to head back down the road for some good times . Take control of your options and make this home yours today! Square footage is approximate and not guaranteed. Buyer responsible for verification.
